sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Inference Client
    participant RBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Server as autogluonserver<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant AG as AutoGluon Engine<br/>(in-process)
    participant StorageInit as Storage Initializer<br/>(init container)
    participant Cloud as Cloud Storage<br/>S3/GCS/Azure<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over StorageInit,Cloud: Flow 2: Model Loading (Pod Init Phase)
    StorageInit->>Cloud: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS IAM / GCP SA / Azure creds
    Cloud-->>StorageInit: Model artifacts
    StorageInit->>StorageInit: Write to /mnt/models

    Note over Server,AG: Server Startup
    Server->>Server: ensure_autogluon_runtime_paths()<br/>Find writable CWD for non-root
    Server->>AG: PredictorDetect: try TimeSeriesPredictor.load()<br/>then TabularPredictor.load()
    AG-->>Server: Model loaded (tabular or timeseries)
    Server->>Server: ModelServer.start()<br/>FastAPI + Uvicorn on 8080

    Note over Client,AG: Flow 1: Tabular Inference (v1 JSON)
    Client->>RBAC: POST /v1/models/{name}:predict<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    RBAC->>RBAC: SubjectAccessReview<br/>Validate token
    RBAC->>Server: POST /v1/models/{name}:predict<br/>HTTP/8080 (localhost)<br/>Pre-authorized
    Server->>Server: Parse JSON instances<br/>Build DataFrame
    Server->>AG: TabularPredictor.predict(df)<br/>or predict_proba(df)
    AG-->>Server: Predictions array
    Server-->>RBAC: JSON response<br/>{"predictions": [...]}
    RBAC-->>Client: JSON response<br/>HTTPS/8443

    Note over Client,AG: Flow 1b: Tabular Inference (v2 Tensor)
    Client->>RBAC: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    RBAC->>Server: Forward (pre-authorized)
    Server->>Server: Map tensor inputs to DataFrame columns<br/>Validate shapes [batch] or [batch,1]
    Server->>AG: TabularPredictor.predict(df)
    AG-->>Server: Predictions
    Server->>Server: Map to v2 InferResponse<br/>Auto-detect output datatype
    Server-->>RBAC: v2 InferResponse
    RBAC-->>Client: v2 InferResponse

    Note over Client,AG: Flow 3: Time Series Inference (v1 JSON only)
    Client->>RBAC: POST /v1/models/{name}:predict<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    RBAC->>Server: Forward (pre-authorized)
    Server->>Server: ensure_autogluon_runtime_paths()<br/>Parse JSON with item_id, timestamp, target
    Server->>AG: TimeSeriesPredictor.predict(ts_df,<br/>known_covariates, use_cache=False)
    AG-->>Server: Forecast DataFrame
    Server->>Server: Convert to JSON (mean + quantiles)
    Server-->>RBAC: JSON response
    RBAC-->>Client: JSON response

    Note over Client,Server: Monitoring
    Client->>Server: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080 (internal)
    Server-->>Client: Prometheus metrics<br/>inference latency, request count
